    "Description": {
      "type": "text",
      "dtype": "String",
      "label": "Metapower Description",
      "value": "<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Every new beginning will find you a little bit more fortunate than the moment before. With Beginner&rsquo;s Luck, you can disperse minor inconveniences from your personal struggles. Using Beginner&rsquo;s Luck is effortless, and you can experience its results in the following seconds after its activation. Disciplined Arbiters can disperse additional minor problems, although not capable yet of using their cosmic luck to mitigate real challenges. As you begin to harness the power of Beginner&rsquo;s Luck, the world around you seems to conspire in your favor, guiding you through the twists and turns of life with a gentle hand.</span></em></p>"
